Package: orderly3.db
Title: Database Support for 'orderly3'
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(person("Rich", "FitzJohn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "rich.fitzjohn@gmail.com"),
             person("Imperial College of Science, Technology and Medicine",
                    role = "cph"))
Description: Access databases from 'orderly3' while running reports.
    Includes the basic 'SQL' support originally included in 'orderly'
    for establishing connections and setting up data for use within a
    report.
